We need to retroactively change the status of people who perpetuated hideous patterns of racism from â€˜heroesâ€™ to â€˜villains.â€™ And villains donâ€™t deserve statues.
Iâ€™m asking the Capitol Commission and the Tennessee Historical Commission to please consider the implications of how hurtful it would be to continue fighting for these monuments.
